pageContext.claim: “Why did the DNC REFUSE to turn over its Server to the FBI, and still hasn't? It's all a big Dem scam and excuse for losing the election!”
pageContext.analysis: The DNC did refuse to give direct access to the FBI, but allowed a third-party company to gather information on behalf of the FBI. Former FBI director James Comey told Congress FBI technicians got all the information they needed without requiring possession of the server.
